{
  "id": 5140168270413824,
  "name": "Device Bound Session Credentials",
  "summary": "To enhance user security and combat session cookie theft, Chrome is introducing [Device Bound Session Credentials (DBSC)](https://developer.chrome.com/docs/web-platform/device-bound-session-credentials). This feature allows websites to bind a user's session to their specific device, which makes it significantly more difficult for stolen session cookies to be used on other machines.",
