      "experiment_goals": "We want overall feedback on the header-based API. Note that error handling during session refresh is complex. It is not yet recommended that sites enforce strictly on the presence of device bound cookies (e.g. logging users out if they're missing). The error rate should be sufficiently low to understand if the API is unclear or overly complex.",
